步驟，並舉例說明之。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00423', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關「一位有才能的管理者所須具備的管理技能」的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["溝通、領導與激勵均屬於人際關係技能（humanrelationshipskill）", "技術性技能（technicalskill）的重要性，隨著管理層級的提升而遞減", "不同階層的管理者，均須具備政治性技能（politicalskill）", "概念性技能（conceptualskill）對於基層管理者的重要性，高於高層管理者"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00424', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '決策依問題性質可分成程式化決策與非程式化決策。有關程式化決策與非程式化決策的敘述，下 列何者錯誤？', '["在問題結構上，程式化決策偏結構化，非程式化決策偏非結構化", "在管理層級上，程式化決策的決策層級較低階，非程式化決策的決策層級較高階", "在資訊上，程式化決策的資訊較易取得，非程式化決策的資訊較為模糊、不完整", "在處理時間上，程式化決策需較長時間處理，非程式化決策可短時間處理"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00425', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '轉型策略為組織完成SWOT分析後可採行的策略之一。有關轉型策略之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["利用存在的外在機會，配合組織的優勢", "利用本身有利的條件來排除外在環境的衝擊或障礙", "藉由把握外在的機會，以降低組織的劣勢型態", "將外部威脅與內部劣勢降到最低，不使情勢繼續惡化"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00426', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關策略性規劃之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["強調穩定取向", "以現在的基礎做為未來的決策藍圖", "聚焦於外在環境，面對不確定的外在環境也可以採取行動", "是一種階段性的過程"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00427', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '團體決策法中，有關「電子會議（electronicmeeting）」的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["以名義團體法，輔以電腦科技而成", "因為要處理設備，電子會議費時且缺乏效率", "是一種團體決策法，但參與者無法匿名", "相關議題討論或投票須待會議後方能進行統計分析"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00428', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於有效的策略行動計畫需具備之要件，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["前瞻性（proactivity）係指對未來採取長期觀點的程度，以及將組織引領到正確方向的程度", "相符性（congruency）係指符合組織特性、外部環境的程度", "分工（divisionoflabor）係指將工作職責指派給工作者，確認工作者能否勝任", "綜效（synergy）係指整合組織各次單位的行動，使其更能達到組織目標"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00429', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '組織的部門分化係指組織基於分工合作的需要，將各層級的業務與權責劃分為水平或橫向的單位。 今若某機構將部門分化為老人組、身心障礙組、兒童組、婦女組等，是依什麼標準來劃分部門？', '["依功能分部化", "依顧客／案主分部化", "依產品／服務分部化", "依地區分部化"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00430', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-113-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '激勵理論認為激勵行為效果與被激勵者的需求能否滿足有關。有關Clayton Alderfer的ERG理論 觀點，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["係從Maslow的需求層次理論簡化修改而來", "成長需求（needsofgrowth）相當於Maslow需求層次中的自尊需求", "生存需求（needsofexistence）相當於Maslow需求層次中的生理需求、安全需求", "關係需求（needsofrelatedness）相當於Maslow需求層次中的歸屬需求"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "890a7ba83f8f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "96773571a3bf", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "103", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
